# PNA header union: parses header union member based on first byte.
# No send_to_port -> all packets drop; exercises header union parsing.

# First byte = 0x00: extract h1 (Hdr1, 1 byte), deparse h1 + union
# h1.a=0x00, then h1 extracted as union member (1 byte)
packet 0 00 AA

# First byte = 0x01: extract h2 (Hdr2, 2 bytes), then setInvalid -> deparse h1 only
packet 0 01 AABB
